  "title": "ANNOUNCEMENT: Azure SQL DB, Always Encrypted with VBS Secure Enclaves",
  "contentHtml": "In this episode Michael talks with guest Pieter Vanhove&nbsp;\n                  (\n                     <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/pieter-vanhove-1756169/'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a>\n                     <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://twitter.com/Pieter_Vanhove'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-x-twitter\"></i></a>\n                  ) \n                  about a new addition to the Always Encrypted family: Always Encrypted with Virtualization-Based Security (VBS) Enclaves. This new feature is available <b>today</b> in Public Preview.\n\n                  <br>\n\n                  <!-- Insert episode info from rss.com into NNNNNN and TTTTTT which is the episode number and the title -->\n                  <iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.rss.com/azsecpodcast/827379?theme=light\" class=\"podcast-player\" title=\"The Azure Security Podcast\" frameborder=\"0\"><a href=\"https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/827379/\">VBS-AE</a></iframe>\n\n                  <h5>Links</h5> \n                  <!-- Links to news articles -->\n                  <ul>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/827379/'>Transcript <i class=\"fa-solid fa-pencil\"></i></a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/azure-sql-blog/vbs-enclaves-for-always-encrypted-in-azure-sql-database-preview/ba-p/3725526\">Preview: VBS Enclaves for Always Encrypted in Azure SQL Database</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-sql/database/always-encrypted-with-secure-enclaves-landing?view=azuresql\">Always Encrypted with secure enclaves documentation</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-sql/database/always-encrypted-enclaves-getting-started?view=azuresql&tabs=azure-portal\">Tutorial: Getting started with Always Encrypted with secure enclaves in Azure SQL Database</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/sql/relational-databases/security/encryption/always-encrypted-database-engine?view=sql-server-ver16\">Always Encrypted</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows-hardware/design/device-experiences/oem-vbs\">Virtualization-based Security (VBS)</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows-server/virtualization/hyper-v/hyper-v-technology-overview\">Hyper-V Technology Overview</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/blog/azure-confidential-computing-on-4th-gen-intel-xeon-scalable-processors-with-intel-tdx/\">(Michael mentioned this, nothing to do with VBS AE) Azure Confidential Computing on 4th Gen Intel Xeon Scalable Processors with Intel TDX</a></li>\n                  </ul>"
